&lt;p>We&amp;rsquo;re developing &lt;strong>interactive applications&lt;/strong> designed to help you explore this wonderful body of textual heritage as you contribute data!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>We need your help with two tasks&lt;/strong>:&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>📍 Locating and/or tag advertisements&lt;/li>
&lt;li>🎮 Transcribing individual words&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Your help will make the newspapers more usable for both humans and machines!&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>The processed text will be made available online for users to search, browse and enjoy.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>The processed text will be used by Eurac Research to improve the searchability of the digitised newspapers.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
