&lt;p>In this custom web game, inspired by &lt;a href="http://typespeed.sourceforge.net/">Typespeed&lt;/a>, words automatically extracted from the digitised Tyrolean newspapers drop from the sky. The goal of the game is simple: you must type the words as fast as possible before the animals reach and kill &lt;a href="https://www.iceman.it/en/the-iceman/">Ötzi the Iceman&lt;/a>! Words typed correctly will scare off the animals and prolong Ötzi&amp;rsquo;s life. &lt;!--When Ötzi dies, you are shown the original newspaper article from which the killing name (the killer!) was taken, allowing you to explore its context.-->&lt;/p>
&lt;!--&lt;div class="alert alert-info d-flex" role="alert">
&lt;div class="flex-shrink-1 alert-icon">👉 &lt;/div>
&lt;div class="w-100">No sign-up or registration required! &lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;br />&lt;br />-->
&lt;div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
